<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n40112a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40112a">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40112a"> 112(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ and he falling / out of his <font color="green">[standing]</font> </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: In Luke 10:18 Jesus says, &ldquo;I saw Satan fall like lightning from heaven.&rdquo; The context of these words is the return of the 70 (or 72) disciples that Jesus had sent out to evangelize and prepare His way to Jerusalem. When the 70 return and give their report, they are joyful and a little surprised that &ldquo;even the demons submit to us in your name&rdquo; (verse 17). Jesus&apos; first words in reply are, &ldquo;I saw Satan fall like lightning from heaven.&rdquo; (verse 18). </mm> </dd></dl>
